Function Interface ''{0}'' uses data type replacement to replace built-in type names with user types that prevent generation of any reusable subsystem code. To generate code for this function interface, set the 'EnableUserReplacementTypes' configuration set parameter to 'off'.

To generate code for this function interface, set configuration set parameter 'CodeReplacementLibrary' to 'None' or to a library that does not support data alignment.

 Block : ''{1}'' 
 Reason : ''{2}''
